            </div>
            <h2>Our Experience</h2>
            <div class="section-description">
                Miron specializes in providing innovative preconstruction, construction management, design-build, general construction, and industrial services to multiple markets. From elementary schools to office buildings to casinos and clinics, we work side-by-side with our clients to bring their dreams to life.             </div>
