<div class="valuesMobileLeft"><img class="shadow" role="img" src="/assets-f/img/6fc26cead17fb8.svg" alt="" width="150" height="150"></div>
<div class="valuesMobileRight">Be authentic, lead with humility and recognize the needs of others. Care for one another and extend a helping hand wherever it’s needed. Honor our history.</div>
