<div class="valuesMobileLeft"><img role="img" class="shadow" src="/assets-f/img/1bbde6cb06c70c.svg" alt="" width="150" height="150"></div>
<div class="valuesMobileRight">Get involved, respond with urgency and work as a team to get the job done. Leverage the strengths of each individual and overcome obstacles as one.</div>
</div></div>
